article_title: Healthcare navigator signs up the metro-east for insurance
article_text:
Melissa O’Neill has been a navigator for three years

Outreach events anchor her in communities

Final push for sign-up during open enrollment is Sunday in Collinsville

article_metadata.news-keywords: healthcare, Affordable Care Act, navigator, Melissa O'Neill, Southern Illinois Healthcare Foundation
article_metadata.description: Melissa O’Neill, a healthcare navigator with the Southern Illinois Healthcare Foundation, is in the home stretch of another open-enrollment period, her third in the three years since the health-insurance marketplace opened in 2013.
